content:
Sounds like your DNS records have not yet been updated to show your new host. Perhaps ask dreamhost as they are the new hosting provider how long that might take. 24 hours is not out of the realms of possibility.

Unless of course your last provider asked you to use their SMTP server not one associated with your registered domain. Then it will appear in the outgoing server (SMTP) in account settings.
